{"tid":2307190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"背包撚請入嚟放低你個背包","createTime":"2020-12-01T04:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T04:49:00.000Z","uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28b4342dcd2f698cbdfdeb0435332f7e7a8dd0e8","tid":2307190,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"一直都好中意孭背囊<br />\n貪佢裝得多嘢<br />\n<br />\n全身gear 銀包 鎖匙 水 衫 外套 尿袋 紙巾咩都好可以放晒入去<br />\n出街有買嘢又可以放埋入去<br />\n基本上大部分可以拎出街嘅嘢都可以塞晒入去<br />\n所以無論返工去飲定去旅行都會孭背囊<br />\n每次出門佢就好似係我條女咁樣樣<br />\n冇咗佢喺身邊就冇咗種安全感<br />\n<br />\n負重可以好多 幾多嘢同幾重都好<br />\n都係用兩個膊頭孭起<br />\n仲可以free番兩隻手出嚟做其他嘢<br />\n<br />\n唔似斜孭或者單邊<br />\n放多少少嘢都好難孭<br />\n<br />\n所以我真係好中意孭我個背囊<br />\n最後放低我條女俾大家睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owjuEh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowjuEh3.jpg&h=910a34c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十家可唔可分享下你個背囊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f23e3b2c740a5ba199b14f2d0506ba3f813ce8","tid":2307190,"uid":308264,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8612581f3350a522cc4965deb2a519a289147a44","tid":2307190,"uid":105802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46PqW7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46PqW7m.jpg&h=19f91ffa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84f24180d23b4b5d0ad0f9bcb303c6b73c1ba233","tid":2307190,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f23e3b2c740a5ba199b14f2d0506ba3f813ce8","tid":2307190,"uid":308264,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"用唔用到三十年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c1b473b684662074c84654b94291543eb576ac","tid":2307190,"uid":45830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":